data.description: Welcome to your beautifully updated 2-bed, 2-bath condo in Pinole's Willowbrook Complex. This private ground level unit features modern comforts and a prime location, adjacent to a scenic walking trail and creek. Inside you'll find a fresh palette with new paint, laminate flooring and updated kitchen, creating an inviting atmosphere. The open-concept design flows seamlessly from the updated kitchen to the dining and living areas. Convenience abounds with in-unit laundry, wood burning fireplace and ample storage. The Willowbrook complex provides access to a full gym, sparkling pool, and spa. This tranquil unit comes with a detached 1-car garage and is close to I80, Highway 4, shopping, restaurants and BART. Don't miss this opportunity—schedule your viewing today!
